with the 4 swords? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/umangurabok.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Mangurabok</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(3/30/02 6:26:08 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4586.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Epic questions</span><hr size=1> no you do not have to be level 50 to pp the notes, i have my neriak and am working on kaladim and i am sub 50.   <br>
