reenFromWeb?topicID=4586.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Epic questions</span><hr size=1> Got the note from Founy. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->   <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#2f2f4f><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub35.ezboard.com/ubacstaberindaback.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Bacstaber Indaback</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(4/1/02 1:33:06 am)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub35.ezboard.com/fthesafehousefrm13.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=4586.topic&index=10>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Epic questions</span><hr size=1> I got my note from the dorf at lvl 43 with pick skill of 200, it only took me about a half hour. Now I am working on the neriak one and I have to bring cleric for rezes =P Was there for about 2 hours at 45 and didnt get, but I am 47 now so I am planing to go back and try. To answer you question.. I dont think yuo can talk to quest NPC's before 50 although I havent tried, but you are defenitely able to get notes and some other stuff (book from hate , ect.) pre lvl 50. I am approching 50 as well and I'm looking forward to the ubbah wep =) Good luck to you!<br>
